  "detailed_description": "Immerse yourself in exciting adventures in the world of portal physics!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082950/extras/03a5422ef43d4fae12bede1d29e523df.poster.avif?t=1729703340\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082950/extras/03a5422ef43d4fae12bede1d29e523df.webm?t=1729703340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082950/extras/03a5422ef43d4fae12bede1d29e523df.mp4?t=1729703340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In this 3D platformer, you have to solve puzzles using a portal gun to overcome obstacles and move forward. Explore bizarre locations, activate mechanisms and, through clever use of portals, open the way to new levels.<br><br>Face challenges that require logic and dexterity to navigate twisting mazes to reach the finish line. Each new stage will give you even more puzzles and opportunities to show your skills.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082950/extras/bf7da7f0d33e7976c652e84f0ca993a0.poster.avif?t=1729703340\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082950/extras/bf7da7f0d33e7976c652e84f0ca993a0.webm?t=1729703340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082950/extras/bf7da7f0d33e7976c652e84f0ca993a0.mp4?t=1729703340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Immerse yourself in exciting gameplay where portal physics will be your key to victory. Challenge yourself by solving puzzles and discover new worlds beyond the ordinary!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\